  • Method Details

    • onEventAdded

      void onEventAdded(String name, String date, String facility, String registrationEndDate, String description, int maxWaitEntrants, int maxSampleEntrants, String posterUri, boolean isGeolocate, String waitlistedMessage, String enrolledMessage, String cancelledMessage, String invitedMessage)
      Callback for adding a new event with the provided details.
      Parameters:
      name - Name of the event.
      date - Date of the event.
      facility - Facility for the event.
      registrationEndDate - Registration end date.
      description - Description of the event.
      maxWaitEntrants - Maximum number of waitlist entrants.
      maxSampleEntrants - Maximum number of sample entrants.
      posterUri - URI of the uploaded poster image.
      isGeolocate - Geolocation status.
      waitlistedMessage - Notification message for waitlisted entrants.
      enrolledMessage - Notification message for enrolled entrants.
      cancelledMessage - Notification message for cancelled entrants.
      invitedMessage - Notification message for invited entrants.
